com.aylanetworks.aylasdk.plugin

接口 AylaPlugin

  • 所有已知子接口:
    AylaLocalDeviceManager, DeviceClassPlugin
    所有已知实现类:
    AylaBLEDeviceManager

    public interface AylaPlugin
    AylaPlugin is the base interface for the Ayla Mobile SDK plugin system. Plugins may be installed in the SDK via calls to AylaNetworks.installPlugin(String, AylaPlugin). Any object implementing this interface may be installed as a plugin. The objects will be called via the AylaPlugin interfaces when the SDK is initialized, paused, resumed or shut down. Installed plugins may be obtained from the AylaNetworks singleton object by calling AylaNetworks.getPlugin(String).
